Endo, Konuma, Sakurai on Japan Firms' Competitiveness

-- B y  
-- 
2011-10-20T08:08:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/endo-konuma-sakurai-on-japan-firms-competitiveness-video-.html
Koji Endo, an analyst at Advanced 
Research  Japan , Yasuyuki Konuma, executive officer and director 
of new listings at  Tokyo  Stock Exchange Inc., and  Yuuki Sakurai ,
president at Fukoku Capital Management, talk about the 
competitiveness of Japanese companies, the nation's economy and 
damages caused by the March 11 earthquake and tsunami.  Bloomberg's John Brinsley moderated the panel at the 
"Bloomberg Link Japan Conference: Road to Recovery" in Tokyo 
yesterday. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 39:16
 